 <description>&lt;p&gt;
Hello there,&lt;br /&gt;
Our course has come to an end! I hope you guys were able to share your knowledge with the other peers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;#39;m currently in Barcelona at the P2PU Techsprint, and we&amp;#39;re working on the improved version of P2PU.&lt;br /&gt;
