<item>
 <title>[Class 6] Prototyping/Mock-up</title>
 <link>http://archive.p2pu.org/webcraft/ux-designing-education/discussion/class-6-prototypingmock</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;-------------------------------------&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Class 6 - Prototyping/Mock-up&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Propose a new user experience design to the P2PU Webcraft platform. Use graphical tools, as Balsamiq or Mockingbirs, to do the graphical wireframes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	An important detail:&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;strong&gt;This is a real project&lt;/strong&gt;. The ideas developed here will be presented to the P2PU project team, on a Creative Commons Attribution model.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Let&amp;#39;s work together, I&amp;#39;m sure there&amp;#39;s gonna be lots of great ideas.&lt;br /&gt;
	--------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;
