<item>
 <title>[Class 5] UX Design plan</title>
 <link>http://archive.p2pu.org/webcraft/ux-designing-education/discussion/class-5-ux-design-plan</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;
Hello everyone!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On our last class, we studied about using Personas as methodological tool to help on the Design process. Now, we&amp;#39;re starting the development of our final virtual learning environment. This activity will be done in parts - Class 5, Class 6 and - the final presentation - Class 7.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This class will be slightly different from the others. The motive/theme will come from yourselves. I&amp;#39;ll be here as an orientator, helping you to discuss and analyze deep questions about user experience design.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
