 <title>[Class 3] Introduction to Cognitive science and Gestalt principles</title>
 <link>http://archive.p2pu.org/webcraft/ux-designing-education/discussion/class-3-introduction-cognitive-science-and-gestalt-principles</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;
Hello everyone, this is the brief for our third class.&lt;br /&gt;
As posted earlier, there are going to be different assignments/exercises/reading recommendations thru the week. Please post your results here in this Forum thread till Sunday October 2nd.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-------------------------&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Class 3 - Exercise 1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Read these links about Gestalt, Cognitive sciences and the Theory of Perception. Post your comments here in the forum. You&amp;#39;ll realize that the authors of these articles have different perspectives about the efficiency of these concepts.&lt;/p&gt;
