 <title>[Class 2] Introduction to Interaction, Information, Interface and Instructional Design</title>
 <link>http://archive.p2pu.org/webcraft/ux-designing-education/discussion/class-2-introduction-interaction-information-interface-and-instructional-design</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;
Hello everyone,&lt;br /&gt;
This is the brief for our second class. Please note that classes from now on will last 1 week, with one or more activities/assignments to be published during the days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-------------------------&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Class 2 - Exercise 1&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
